{"meta":{"authors":[{"id":"6","fullname":"Nicolas Tournadre"}],"title":"","dates":{"created_at":"2013-09-15 04:14:24 UTC","updated_at":"2013-09-15 04:14:24 UTC"}},"nodes":[{"index":0,"parent_index":-1,"body":"<p class=\"Paragraph\">The perfective past tense is formed by placing after the verb the expressions <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">པ་རེད་</span> (assertive), <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">པ་ཡིན་</span> (intentional egophoric), or <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སོང་</span> (testimonial).</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">In English these forms can be translated by the past or sometimes by the present perfect.</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">The forms<span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"> པ་ཡིན་ </span>/ <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">པ་རེད་</span> are composed of the suffix <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">པ་</span> followed by the essential copula <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">རེད་ </span>or <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཡིན་</span>. The intentional form <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">པ་ཡིན་ </span>may only be used with volitional verbs in the first person.</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">In interrogative sentences that contain no interrogative pronoun (where, who, why, what, etc.), the egophoric form <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">པ་ཡིན་</span> is replaced by པས་; in sentences where there is an interrogative pronoun, <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">པ་ཡིན་</span> is replaced by <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">པ་</span>.</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">The auxiliary<span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"> པ་རེད་</span> is used in narratives and stories, which is why it is sometimes described as the &ldquo;narrative past.&rdquo; The various forms are as follows:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>&middot; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ང་ནང་ལ་བསྡད་པ་ཡིན།</span> &ldquo;I stayed at home.&rdquo; (egophoric)</li>\n<li>&middot; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཉི་མ་ནང་ལ་བསྡད་པ་རེད།</span> &ldquo;Nyima stayed at home.&rdquo; (assertive)</li>\n<li>&middot; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཉི་མ་ནང་ལ་བསྡད་སོང་།</span> &ldquo;Nyima stayed at home.&rdquo; (testimonial)</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><strong>Table: The Perfective Past</strong></p>\n<table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"113\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Affirmative</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"132\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Interrogative</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">(without pronouns)</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"113\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Interrogative</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">(with pronouns)</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"113\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Negative</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"113\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Negative Interrogative</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"113\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">པ་ཡིན་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"132\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">པ་ཡིན་པས་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"113\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">པ་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"113\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">མ་</span> + V **</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"113\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">མ་</span> + V + <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">པས་</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"113\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སོང་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"132\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སོང་ངས་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"113\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སོང་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"113\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">མ་སོང་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"113\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">མ་སོང་ངས་</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"113\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">པ་རེད་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"132\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">པ་རེད་པས་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"113\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">པ་རེད་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"113\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">མ་</span> + V + <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">པ་རེད་</span> **</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"113\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">མ་</span> + V + <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">པ་རེད་པས་</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Note: The negative forms that are marked in the table with a **, as well as the corresponding interronegative forms, are rarely used, and other forms such as the perfect are usually preferred. The simple past forms may be used to emphasize the subject&rsquo;s refusal to perform the action: &ldquo;I/he didn&rsquo;t go (even though I/he was supposed to).&rdquo;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཉི་མ་མ་ཕྱིན་པ་རེད།</span> &ldquo;Nyima did not go.&rdquo; </li>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ང་མ་ཕྱིན།</span> &ldquo;I did not go.&rdquo;</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Affirmative</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Interrogative</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">(without pronouns)</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Interrogative</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">(with pronouns)</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Negative</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Negative Interrogative</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">པ་ཡིན་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">པ་ཡིན་པས་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">པ་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">མ་</span> + V **</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">མ་</span> + V + <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">པས་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སོང་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སོང་ངས་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སོང་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">མ་སོང་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">མ་སོང་ངས་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">པ་རེད་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">པ་རེད་པས་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">པ་རེད་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">མ་</span> + V + <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">པ་རེད་</span> **</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">མ་</span> + V + <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">པ་རེད་པས་</span></p>\n","title":""}]}